         MACRO
&L       $VGET &ID
.*
.*       THIS MACRO WORKS WITH THE VGETSUB MACRO TO ACQUIRE
.*       AN ISPF VARIABLE FROM THE ISPF VARIABLE POOL AND
.*       ALLOW THIS PROGRAM TO ACCESS IT
.*
*
*        CALL ISPF AND MAKE VARIABLE &ID AVAILABLE
*        UPON RETURN R1 POINTS TO THE DATA
*
         LCLA  &LEN
&LEN     SETA  K'&ID
&L       MVC   $ID(&LEN),=C'&ID'
         BAL   R14,VGETSUB
         MVC   $ID,=CL8' '         RESET $ID FOR NEXT USE
         MEND
